content: Do I need to sort a Vec before building a BinaryHeap from it ? Depending on whether I sort it or not, I appear to be getting two different BinaryHeaps.

what do you mean by "different BinaryHeaps"? there are many different ways to put the same set of elements into a binary heap, and all of them work the same with the heap interface (pop() removes elements in order), but e.g. iteration and Debug printing is arbitrary either way

iteration and Debug printing is arbitrary either way

I was comparing them with debug printing -.-
